<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. وَتَكْلِيمُ هَذَا النُّوعِ لَيْسَ بِرَائِبِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَحَنَّ لَهُ الْجِذْعُ الْقَدِيمُ تَحَزُّنًا<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فَإِنَّ فِرَاقَ الْحُبِّ أَدْهَى الْمَصَائِبِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَأَعْجَبُ تِلْكَ الْبَدْرُ يَنْشَقُ عِنْدَهُ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَمَا هُوَ فِي إِعْجَازِهِ مِنْ عَجَائِبِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَشَقَّ لَهُ جِبْرِيلُ بَاطِنَ صَدْرِهِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>لِغَسْلِ سَوَادٍ بِالسُّوَيْدَاءِ لازِبِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَأَسْرَى عَلَى مَتْنِ الْبُرَاقِ إِلَى السَّمَا<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>فَيَا خَيْرَ مَرْكُوبٍ وَيَا خَيْرَ رَاكِبِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَرَاعَتْ بَلِيغُ الآيِ كُلَّ مُجَادِلٍ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>خَصِيمٍ تَمَادَى فِي مِرَاءِ الْمَطَالِبِ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>بَرَاعَةُ أُسْلُوبٍ وَعَجْزُ مُعَارِضٍ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>بَلاغَةُ أَقْوَالِ وَأَخْبَارُ غَائِبِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَسَمَّاهُ رَبُّ الْخَلْقِ أَسْمَاءَ مِدْحَةٍ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>تُبَيِّنُ مَا أَعْطَى لَهُ مِنْ مَنَاقِبِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>رَؤُوفٌ رَحِيمٌ أَحْمَدٌ وَمُحَمَّدٌ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>مُقَفَى وَمِفْضَالٌ يُسَمَّى بِعَاقِبِ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>إِذَا مَا أَثاَرُوا فِتْنَةً جَاهِلِيَّةً<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>يَقُودُ بِبَحْرٍ زَاخِرٍ مِنْ كَتَائِبِ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>يَقُومُ لِدَفْعِ الْبَأْسَ أَسْرَعَ قَوْمِهِ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>بِجَيْشٍ مِن الأَبْطَالِ غُرِّ السَّلاهِبِ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>